CS_MountainAbode_Lith:
	
Save, or defend, the hostages in this roomy mountain mansion, with a view.

INSTALLATION:
Extract this .zip into your your 

"C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\"Source E-mail\counter-strike source\cstrike\"

It will ask you to overwrite some files, just say yes, it only says that cause of the 
folder that are being extracted.
